description:
YouTube is an incredibly popular channel as more people are becoming accustomed to utilizing YouTube as a channel for consume content and learn more. As the content creators, it's critical we learn how to rank our videos for those primary keywords that are most critical. In this course, people will learn the following:

  • Introduction To YouTube Platform
  • YouTube SEO Ranking Factors
  • How To Create A Great Video
  • Video On Page Optimization
  • How To Attract Views & Links On Your Video
  • Ranking Your “YouTube” Videos On Google

At the end of this course, you will have the full confidence to rank any videos you create on YouTube or any other platform for that matter.
title: YouTube Search Video SEO Marketing: Rank On YouTube & Google
